Package com.diy.hardware

Class CoinTray

java.lang.Object
com.unitedbankingservices.AbstractDevice<IDeviceObserver>
com.diy.hardware.CoinTray
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDevice<IDeviceObserver>, Sink<Coin>
public class CoinTray extends AbstractDevice<IDeviceObserver> implements Sink<Coin>
Simulates the tray where dispensed coins go for the user to collect them. It is a passive device requiring no power, being gravity-fed.
